title: The Artie Quitter Podcast AUG 19 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Gino Bisconti, Sue Costello  and Chris Cotton, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.



TODAY's SHOW  (01:08:14)

Artie, Joe Matarese & Gino Bisconti are joined on the phone by American stand-up comedian, actor, voice-over artist, and author, Jim Gaffigan.  
Artie talks to Jim Gaffigan about his new TV show, and is reminded of a time he was concerned about having been hard on Jeremy Piven in front of comedian/actor Adam Goldberg
